  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a study to validate the utility and accuracy of the non-invasive device (LiDCOrapid
      monitor) during a period of phlebotomy and graded blood loss in patients who are having
      cardiac surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
